{"tid":1256870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係真心㗎","createTime":"2019-06-25T08:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T16:11:18.000Z","uid":266134,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8524eb533cef8066f0f9d1ba60cf5c63b40dc8","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:58:35.000Z","msg":"對於今日嘅道歉運動，有人覺得係關公嘢，但作為圍税局嘅一員，可以再大家講我每句唔好意思都係出自真心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwbQNoa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwbQNoa.png&h=b0cd3d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論閣下尋日係去税局返工定交嘢，對唔住，我哋的確阻到你哋，唔好意思，請你哋繼續支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVQx0J0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVQx0J0.png&h=e67ad90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有部份市民反而覺得對唔住我哋，其實冇話邊個對唔住邊個，只要為香港好，大家都係做緊啱嘅事。不過有少少請求，希望各位父母可以教育下一代，唔一定要抗爭到底，但要不平則嗚；唔一定要想法獨到，但一定要獨立思考；唔一定要做叻人，但要做好人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sq7P2Zn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSq7P2Zn.png&h=423fde4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋教你哋嘅下一代，下一代教佢哋嘅下一代，不斷loop......一個良好循環好重要，過去嘅事改變唔到，只可以未來做好啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gq837rm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGq837rm.png&h=d70cee69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋真係愛香港㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qOon0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qOon0Q.png&h=b389ef05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"dae48d2e5924fce21cff80fc3b74cb33f625440e","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c59abe147a278bf44935fc31058811fc588daed","tid":1256870,"uid":267342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7c140da0ca15fb56d4cc265f6c4716eb4f8b70","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d49ede06e62410b4f2d586102ae9e9aa153b86","tid":1256870,"uid":55425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"dd342bb55c158830dd2198a7160e68f7a030c35a","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95a9d5e305c2d5f79865f9cac281d493a86bcaf","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cd28280e52bba09bbd17a4c31599e2e471e0502","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a239fb76454211bea493a0e3a754b9b4a3d8f47","tid":1256870,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c29496b7ee976dfdf33b3ab9af07b2128753f4e1","tid":1256870,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e87d94b2cb8966c5746fdb81fae38296c9c50ad","tid":1256870,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7853a44422334db95c8fff67131173075ed4559b","tid":1256870,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71773e9b7